stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Parsing: sandbox-broker start

    Parsing --> Probing: policy ok
    Parsing --> Failed: invalid policy

    Probing --> Forking: capability requirements met<br/>(or none required)
    Probing --> Failed: require_landlock + no Landlock<br/>require_bwrap + no bwrap

    Forking --> Foreground_Mode: --foreground flag<br/>or runtime.daemonize=false
    Forking --> Daemon_Spawn: default (daemonize)

    Daemon_Spawn --> Foreground_Mode: child enters here<br/>(parent writes PID, exits 0)

    Foreground_Mode --> Serving: bind UDS<br/>install signal handlers<br/>register cleanup stack

    Serving --> Reloading: SIGHUP
    Reloading --> Serving: policy ok
    Reloading --> Serving: policy invalid<br/>(log + keep running)

    Serving --> Draining: SIGTERM / SIGINT
    Serving --> Draining: stop subcommand

    Draining --> Cleanup: drain timeout (2s)
    Cleanup --> [*]: priority: shutdown listener<br/>then LIFO: pid file → socket → log → audit
    Failed --> [*]: exit 1
